OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers fading during the
OL,7,Fevening, then turning dry overnight
OL,8,Fwith the wind easing. Staying mild for
OL,9,Fmost places although a little cooler
OL,10,Fin rural spots. Cloud will thicken
OL,11,Flater in the night with rain in places
OL,12,Fby dawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FCloud quickly thickens as it
OL,15,Fturns into a rather grey and wet day
OL,16,Ffor most places. Heavy outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain possible in the afternoon and
OL,18,Fevening over western hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
