OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FWet
OL,6,Fand windy weather continues as bands
OL,7,Fof rain move through followed by
OL,8,Fbrighter but showery interludes.
OL,9,FTemperatures dropping down to normal
OL,10,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
